title: Delaware Valley's Hannah Bonaguidi is the lehighvalleylive Girls Cross Country Athlete of the Week
text:
Hannah Bonaguidi , Delaware Valley 
The Delaware Valley senior won the Hunterdon/Warren/Sussex championship Thursday at the Phillipsburg Athletic Complex in 18 minutes, 40 seconds. It was the first individual county cross country championship ever won by a Terrier girl. 
Honorable Mention: Jr. Sydney Brannon , Wilson; Jr. Anna DiMarcello, North Hunterdon; So. Sophie Doman , Palisades; So. Molly Tarvin , Northwestern Lehigh; Fr. L auren Wagner, Voorhees; Jr. Allyson Yanega , Southern Lehigh. 
Brad Wilson may be reached at bwilson@lehighvalleylive.com . Follow him on Twitter @bradwsports . Find Lehigh Valley high school sports on Facebook .
